The plan:

Classes:

Library:
  ZValue    ->   Possible values for the VM
  Zoe       ->   The virtual machine
  Stack     ->   The VM stack
  Bytecode  ->   Helps to create a bytecode
  Compiler  ->   Compile original code into some format (ex. bytecode)

Executable
  Options   ->   Commandline arguments
  REPL      ->   A REPL


Types:
nil       ZNil       null
bool      ZBoolean   bool
int       ZInteger   int64_t
float     ZFloat     double
string    ZString    string
function  ZFunction  
userdata?
thread?
array     ZArray     array
table     ZTable     map

Order of business:
- Makefile + main
- Executable
- Library
